'''Mythcon 26''' was the twenty-sixth annual [[Mythopoeic Society]] conference. 

*'''Theme: "'''Fairies in the Garden, Monsters at the Mall: Fantasy in the World Around Us"
*'''Guests of Honor:''' Tim Powers (fantasy author) and Michael R. Collings (Lewis and fantasy scholar)
*'''Chairman:''' Eleanor M. Farrell
